  "notes": "Healer and priestess, not a front-line fighter. Heal 3 for minor wounds, Heal Body for critical injuries. Charisma rune spell makes her socially unstoppable for 15 minutes. Earth Elemental (summoned via rune magic, costs 1-3 rune points for small/medium/large) can be game-changing. Half-sister of Vasana.",
